## Stack

Electron 41 desktop app (Mac arm64/x64, Windows x64). Renderer: ES modules bundled with esbuild (`public/js/app.bundle.mjs`). Main process: `main.js`. LAN HTTP/WS server: `server.js` on port **3738**. Clinical DB: SQLCipher via `better-sqlite3-multiple-ciphers` + Argon2 (`lib/db/`). Tests: `node --test` (colocated `*.test.mjs` / `*.test.js`).

